478
00:18:42,420 --> 00:18:43,831
You're her father?

479
00:18:43,855 --> 00:18:45,332
Hector Rodriguez.

480
00:18:45,356 --> 00:18:46,500
Do you mind if we come in

481
00:18:46,524 --> 00:18:48,369
