509
00:19:43,720 --> 00:19:44,931
Do you know where she is?

510
00:19:44,955 --> 00:19:46,165
We had a fight.

511
00:19:46,189 --> 00:19:47,435
She took off.

512
00:19:47,459 --> 00:19:49,325
